{"tid":1744801,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"ifc「和你lunch」劉公子撐場","createTime":"2019-11-22T02:16:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T01:48:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"aadd87c5c1eb7530d9ed32c6c966a77fc920094d","tid":1744801,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T02:16:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191122/UUZBN6HRARNPCGC3AQRO3GAZ2U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191122%2FUUZBN6HRARNPCGC3AQRO3GAZ2U%2F&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt8wWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=30bbeb07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191122%2FUUZBN6HRARNPCGC3AQRO3GAZ2U%2F&h=4480570e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191122/UUZBN6HRARNPCGC3AQRO3GAZ2U/</a><br />\n<br />\nifc「和你lunch」劉公子撐場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】多間大學近日先後被警方攻擊，大批大專院校學生、甚至未成年人士被捕，中環人連日發起「和你lunch」，快閃地點首度選址室內的國際金融中心商場（ifc）。早年因拍下警察及藝人肉照惹上官非的同志富商「劉公子」劉定成亦有現身，與眾人一起爭取五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：警違《基本法》侵犯出入境自由<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191122/large/1574354271_b7b8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191122%2Flarge%2F1574354271_b7b8.gif&h=31cfdeff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n戴太陽眼鏡和口罩的劉定成（中）昨現身並高叫口號。<br />\n高叫「解散警隊」<br />\n<br />\n防暴警察中午在畢打街的行人天橋駐守。據現場消息指，因應警方早已佈防，為免「影響心情」，遂改為於ifc聚集，亦貫徹「be water」精神。接近下午2時，現場已有近300人聚集，並開始高叫「Save Hong Kong Sign the Bill」的新口號，希望美國總統特朗普能簽署，讓《香港人權與民主法案》正式成為法律。<br />\n<br />\n戴上太陽黑鏡和口罩的劉定成昨亦低調現身在人群中，他穿着印有「香港」字樣的T恤，高舉象徵五大訴求的五隻手指，高叫「解散警隊，刻不容緩」。<br />\n<br />\n參與「和你lunch」的何小姐指，反送中運動的抗爭持續將近半年，政府仍不願正面回應，警方甚至完全無視所有規矩，「攻城」衝入大學引起公憤。<br />\n<br />\n■記者于健民、張雅婷"},{"pid":"4df44dfe20601e274feb1e9605da5b7bd2c89b9e","tid":1744801,"uid":147047,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T02:20:28.000Z","msg":"想睇多d黑京裸照<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要年紀大d, 有肉地的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42310b893a05282d2c28115d3ea2d8bb15c25d87","tid":1744801,"uid":169665,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T02:21:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NLD6dPw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNLD6dPw.jpg&h=07da4edc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉公子至愛既港島總區行動部高級警司吳樂俊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98957e0f71b992cd3a7d8911b805f7b252bb2d6","tid":1744801,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T02:22:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ced8962474826ed82ed452899780b00406eb64","tid":1744801,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T02:22:25.000Z","msg":"【新款自殺方法】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1744739\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1744739</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e4630890ecd3963b6c4629e3b7c6bee3789567c9","tid":1744801,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T02:22:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f28d44522c841136a29ad02427e43cc86ae4508","tid":1744801,"uid":3241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"42310b893a05282d2c28115d3ea2d8bb15c25d87","tid":1744801,"uid":169665,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T02:21:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NLD6dPw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNLD6dPw.jpg&h=07da4edc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉公子至愛既港島總區行動部高級警司吳樂俊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T02:22:37.000Z","msg":"有冇肉照睇？"},{"pid":"5cd55826